article.description: — Jamal Bieniemy had 21 points as UTEP beat Florida A&M 67-53 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Bieniemy scores 21 to carry UTEP past Florida A&M 67-53
article.linkText: Bieniemy scores 21 to carry UTEP past Florida A&M 67-53
article.story: EL PASO, Texas -- — Jamal Bieniemy had 21 points as UTEP beat Florida A&M 67-53 on Wednesday night. Jorell Saterfield had 14 points for UTEP (4-2). Jamari Sibley added 13 points and seven rebounds. Keonte Kennedy had 12 points and nine rebounds. MJ Randolph had 17 points for the Rattlers (1-3). Kamron Reaves added 13 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
